      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TINKER AMINA (7) was in the minors two back (17.70) at this track but ran below best last time there, finishing 6th. Strong form has emerged from her last run. Better than the latest effort and deserves another chance. BLACK BEETLE (3) has some solid form under his belt and proved too strong last time to win by 2 lengths at this track in a handy 17.86 beating Without Me. Leading player again. BEDAZZLED JEWEL (1) is a fast beginner who has shown good improvement at her last two starts, most recently finishing 2nd at this track over 300m. Expected to be in this for a long way. RUBY ON SCOTCH (4) is going well, finishing in the placings twice in a row. Not beaten far last time when a nose second (17.76) in a Grade 4 at this track.",
